course.subject: MATH
course.name: Partial Differential Equations (Part II)
course.description: This is the second half of a year long introductory graduate course on Partial Differential Equations (PDEs). We will study nonlinear first order PDEs by characteristics, introduction to Hamilton-Jacobi equations and conservation laws, parabolic second order equations, as well as Navier-Stokes equations if time permits.
